<lb n="0507a05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0507a06" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0507002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔西天譯經〕－【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><note n="0507002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">西天譯經【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】，宋西天譯經【明】</note><app n="0507002"><lem wit="【大】">西天譯經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">宋西天譯經</rdg></app>三<note n="0507003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">藏＋（法師）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0507003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藏【大】，藏法師【宋】【元】</note><app n="0507003"><lem wit="【大】">藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">藏法師</rdg></app><note n="0507004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔朝散…臣〕十三字－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0507004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（朝散…臣）十三字【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app cb:word-count="13" n="0507004"><lem wit="【大】">朝散大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0507a07" ed="T"/>明教大師臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0507a08" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT20p0507a0801">爾時世尊告阿難言。世間眾生昧<note n="0507005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">於＝于【明】</note><note n="0507005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於【大】，于【明】</note><app n="0507005"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">于</rdg></app>實智。輪
<lb n="0507a09" ed="T"/>迴三界不知苦本。恣身口意造四重罪如是
<lb n="0507a10" ed="T"/>之人深可憐愍。我有十八<note n="0507a1001" resp="CBETA" type="add">臂【CB】，腎【大】</note><app n="0507a1001"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">臂<note type="cf1">T20n1118_p0507a04</note><note type="cf2">T20n1118_p0507a13</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">腎</rdg></app>大陀羅尼。若有
<lb n="0507a11" ed="T"/>眾生得此陀羅尼常持誦者。是人所作根本
<lb n="0507a12" ed="T"/>罪業皆悉除滅。復能積集無量功德。爾時世
<lb n="0507a13" ed="T"/>尊即說十八臂陀羅尼曰。</p>
